FELINE SPONGIFORM ENCEPHALOPATHY
================================
[1]
Date: Fri, 7 Jun 1996 11:17:31 +0200
To: promed-ahead@usa.healthnet.org
From: chwalzer@ping.at (Chris Walzer)
Having picked up the following from a message to the list from Torsten Brinch:
"Transmissions of scrapie-like disease from kudu, nyala and *CATS* have
already given closely similar results to BSE, suggesting a common infection
source."
I would like to know if there is more information/literature available
concerning Scrapie-Like disease in cats.
Chris
